{"word":"G1877 - ἐπανάγω - epanágō - ep-an-ag'-o - Launch out","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπανάγω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epanágō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-an-ag'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Launch out</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தள்ளு, திரும்பிவா"},{"paragraph":"1. to lead up upon"},{"paragraph":"2. to lead back"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G321 - ἀνάγω - anágō - an-ag'-o/321\">G321</a>; to <i>lead up on</i>, that is, (technically) to <i>put out</i> (to sea); (intransitively) to <i>return:</i> - launch (thrust) out, return.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}